title: Age Is Just A Number!
description:
In this episode, Jessi and Stew sit down with Brynn Crockett, owner of Shade Nine Studio in American Fork, UT. Brynn chased her dreams at a young age and is now a successful stylist and salon owner despite some thinking she would be in over her head. Jessi and Stew share their thoughts on this topic and share some insight as well!
